## Componentes

### Button

```jsx
// Variantes disponibles
primary: 'bg-sage text-white hover:bg-sage/90'
secondary: 'bg-sand text-deep hover:bg-sand/80 border border-sage/20'
outline: 'border border-sage text-sage hover:bg-sage hover:text-white'
ghost: 'text-sage hover:bg-sage/10'
danger: 'bg-red-600 text-white hover:bg-red-700'

// Tamaños
sm: 'px-3 py-1.5 text-sm'
md: 'px-4 py-2 text-sm'
lg: 'px-6 py-3 text-base'
```

### Card

```jsx
// Estilo base
className="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6"
```

### Layout

```jsx
// DashboardLayout
<div className="min-h-screen bg-sand">
  <Navbar />
  <Sidebar />
  <main className="pt-16 ml-64 p-6">
```

