## Patrones de Estilo

### Inputs
```jsx
className="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sage focus:border-transparent"
```

### Listas
```jsx
className="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 divide-y divide-gray-100"
```

### Badges/Tags
```jsx
className="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-sage/10 text-sage"
```

### Estados de Cita
- Completada: `#8CA48F` (sage)
- Pendente: `#D58E6E` (terracotta)
- Cancelada: `#FF6B6B` (error)
- En Proceso: `#A2B2C2` (muted)

---

## Responsive

- Mobile: < 640px
- Tablet: 640px - 1024px
- Desktop: > 1024px
- Sidebar: `ml-264` cuando abierto

---

## Animaciones

```css
.animate-slide-in {
  animation: slide-in 0.3s ease-out;
}

@keyframes slide-in {
  from {
    transform: translateX(100%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translateX(0);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}
```
